file.title: AMM PART II-1285 - TEMPORARY REVISION LIST

page.data: AIRCRAFT MAINTENANCE MANUAL TEMPORARY REVISION LIST This list is intended to show the operator which temporary revisions are applicable to his fleet. The list consists of the temporary revision number, the related issue date, the incorporation date, and the affected subject. S* INDICATES TR HAS BEEN SUPERSEDED BY THE TR REFERRED TO.
